===Etymology===
{{OF.}} [[entre]], ''[[among]]'' + [[tenir]], ''to [[hold]]''

===Pronunciation===
*(''[[Received Pronunciation|UK]]'') {{IPA|/ˌɛntəˈteɪn/}}, {{SAMPA|/%Ent@"teIn/}}
